title: 63. Papcock
description:
Wow it's the 63rd episode! On today's show, Chris talks about having a bunch of kids. Also discussed: Conor McGregor, a Cuban Uber driver, not knowing what day it is, the tediousness of being on set, people who do their own stunts, Eminem, & Chris answers a bunch of questions from Twitter.
